Data files (CSV, JSON, GeoJSON) in the `assets/data/` directory are dedicated to the
**Public Domain** under **CC0 1.0 Universal** (CC0 1.0) where legally possible.

No Copyright: <https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/>

