## Attribution

When using content from the Tigray Knowledge Base, please provide attribution as follows:

**For Academic/Research Use:**

```
Source: Tigray Knowledge Base, Ternafit NGO (2025). 
Available at: https://tigray.ternafit.org
```

**For Media/Journalism:**

```
Information from the Tigray Knowledge Base by Ternafit NGO (https://tigray.ternafit.org)
```

**For Data/Datasets:**

```
Data source: Tigray Knowledge Base - [Dataset Name]
URL: https://tigray.ternafit.org
License: CC0 1.0 (Public Domain)
```

